8 distribution service" means the delivery of electricity to an eligible
9 customer by an incumbent electricity supplier over the incumbent
10 electricity supplier's transmission and distribution systems.
11 (b) The term does not include electric supply service.
12 Sec. 8. (a) Beginning July 1, 2027, an eligible customer of an
13 incumbent electricity supplier may elect to receive:
14 (1) electric supply service directly from a competitive
15 electricity supplier; and
16 (2) transmission and distribution service from the incumbent
17 electricity supplier;
