21 demand response programs, and any other programs outside
22 the provision of basic service.
23 (5) Account or program credits.
24 (6) Taxes.
25 (7) Account management and billing fees.
26 (8) Any other applicable charges or fees.
27 (b) Before July 1, 2027, an incumbent electricity supplier shall:
28 (1) take appropriate internal operational measures to
29 separate the incumbent electricity supplier's costs so as to
