32 after June 30, 2027, under subsection (a);
33 (2) amend all existing approved retail tariffs to reflect these
34 itemized charges and fees and post the tariffs, as amended, on
35 the incumbent electricity supplier's website; and
36 (3) file the amended tariffs with the commission.
37 Upon receiving an incumbent electricity supplier's amended retail
38 tariffs under subdivision (3), the commission shall post the
